# The 3-Layer Architecture (STRICT)

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                      UI LAYER                                │
│  src/app/*, src/components/*                                │
│  • React Server/Client Components                           │
│  • useQuery for reads, useMutation for writes               │
│  • NO database imports, NO business logic                   │
└─────────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                              │ Server Actions
                              ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                     ACTION LAYER                             │
│  src/server/actions/*                                       │
│  • Auth checks: auth() from Clerk                           │
│  • Validation: Zod schemas                                  │
│  • DB Connection: await dbConnect()                         │
│  • Calls Service Layer only                                 │
│  • Returns: ActionResponse<T>                               │
└─────────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                              │ Service calls
                              ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    SERVICE LAYER                             │
│  src/server/services/*                                      │
│  • ONLY place Mongoose models are imported                  │
│  • Pure business logic                                      │
│  • Returns DTOs (plain objects, no Mongoose docs)           │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**NEVER**:
- Import Mongoose models in UI components or Server Actions
- Call `Model.find()` outside the Service Layer
- Skip auth checks in Server Actions
- Return raw Mongoose documents (always convert to DTOs)

